~ start_talk_to_quest
if QuestManager.active_quests.has("my_friend_in_town")
	=> talk_to_steve_in_progress
elif !QuestManager.completed_quests.has("my_friend_in_town")
	=> start
else
	=> already_completed

~ start
Quest Giver: [[Hi|Hello|Howdy]], I've got a quest for you!
Quest Giver: Go talk to my friend Steve to the East in Brady Town.
Quest Giver: He will tell you about the sewers!
- Yeah, sure
	do GameDialogueManager.action_start_quest("my_friend_in_town")
- No thanks.
=> END

~ talk_to_steve_in_progress
Quest Giver: You need to head East to Brady Town to find Steve!
=> END

~ already_completed
Quest Giver: I'm glad you talked to Steve, thats all I've got for now!